  <!-- EN: Kord HMG turret -->
  <DMS_Krepost_KordMG.label>科夫羅夫機槍</DMS_Krepost_KordMG.label>
  <!-- EN: heavy machine gun for mech soldier or infantry support platform.\n\nThis weapon is designed specially for mounted use, so only specific unit can equip it. -->
  <DMS_Krepost_KordMG.description>一種可靠的制式機槍，能夠有效的在遠距離交火中擊穿大部分中小型目標的裝甲並造成殺傷。</DMS_Krepost_KordMG.description>
